{"tid":1205612,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"全 力 一 擊 ！","createTime":"2019-06-11T21:21:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-11T22:39:22.000Z","uid":61264,"like":2,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"c019cf75bc0d3d4ecbec01c0010c935ac974c8a6","tid":1205612,"uid":61264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T21:21:43.000Z","msg":"機場！<br />\n<br />\n點解係機場？<br />\n<br />\n大家認為去機場會分散金鐘既人民力量，所以交比你地考慮<br />\n金鐘人地預左掃都集中掃你，你放幾多人既作用唔大<br />\n多五千人同少五千人影響有限，因為金鐘講緊以萬緊<br />\n反向思考下，大家有人願意去機場<br />\n有機會分散警力之餘，有機會提高關注<br />\n金鐘唔係無用，但如果金鐘係最有用<br />\n上次一百萬人上街就解決左<br />\n當然大家點決定交返比大家<br />\n<br />\n香港國際機場係最多外國人出入既地方<br />\n去機場最大既回響係希望令唔同國藉既人<br />\n等佢地關注，再者有機會聯絡各大大使館<br />\n令到香港政府必須正視及回應<br />\n真係可以仔細諗下<br />\n<br />\n如你有興趣參與行動請加入以下連結<br />\n並等待指示行動<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/DzxX_BXOrY4dCidX2LgAVw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FDzxX_BXOrY4dCidX2LgAVw&d=NC%2FTzFAtl3V7yegmN9swvtLD3cQOkzCKckuFp%2FmPVdU%3D&h=dce61491\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/DzxX_BXOrY4dCidX2LgAVw</a><br />\n<br />\n‼️呼籲唔上前線嘅可以去加入依個<br />\n<br />\n機場唔會冇用 因為機場係香港其中一個命脈<br />\n係一個要塞<br />\n機場出事 官方一定要調派人手<br />\n點會冇用<br />\n<br />\n‼️上前線嘅請繼續上前線"},{"pid":"882fe0dc42f49b4868f1d7e8ef09abdd54449f9a","tid":1205612,"uid":61264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T21:22:12.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f04136ff4e91209f863e24bdef63786de43e58de","tid":1205612,"uid":50835,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T21:22:56.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>請勿轉移視線</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tyT9J3o.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtyT9J3o.png&h=1d343b77&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"da17d41f7b67b8fb48c44690bb98c09e58dace62","tid":1205612,"uid":10023,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T21:23:12.000Z","msg":"死撚